quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  52,32,"Nohomba amaparo kabu niko kabarumanga kario, nohomba bo ni Abandu abafuru butswa?"
  52,33,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Wakasia kano (Ikurani)”, halali bo shibasuubilangasa tawe!"
  52,34,"Mana barerekhwo amakhuwa shinga kano, nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto."
  52,35,"Nohomba shibaalongwakhwo nende shiosishiosi tawe, nohomba bo nibo baloonganga (kata nibelonga abeene)?"
  52,36,"Koo! Nibo baloonga likulu nende eshialo? Halali babula obulaamba tawe."
  52,37,"Nohomba bali nende libishilo lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, nohomba nibo abemeli ba buli eshindu?"
  52,38,"Nohomba bali netsingasi tsiokhurechelesiliakhwo? Mana omurechelesi wabu oyo arerekhwo ebifune bilolekha."
  52,39,"Nohomba Nyasaye ali nabakhana nanyu muli nabasiani?"
  52,40,"Nohomba obarebanga bakhurunge, nabo balolanga obusiro muno okhurunga omurungo oko?"
  52,41,"Nohomba bamanyile akefisa mana bakahandikanga?"
  52,42,"Nohomba benyanga okhukhukholela ebifwanga? Halali balia bakhaya nibo abalakholelwa ebifwanga."
  52,43,"Nohomba bali nende nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye tawe? Nyasaye nomutswenufu ehale nende bia bamutsokasinjia ninabio."
  52,44,"Ne nibalolanga lileesi lieshinyasio nilikwa okhurula hekulu, bakhaboolele mbu ni amalesi kachingane."
  52,45,"Kho baleshe butswa okhuula olwa balibukaana nende inyanga yabu yabalisishilibwamo."
  52,46,"Inyanga ya ebifwanga biabu shibikhabakhoonye shiosishiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe."
  52,47,"Ne toto balia abakhola amabii, balinyoola eshinyasio shindi shilali shino tawe. Ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  52,48,"Ne linda okhubusia omuse khwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Toto ewe oli mutsimoni tsiefu, ne mutswenule khulwokhumwitsomia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa oba niwema."
  52,49,"Ne eshilo khandi omutswenule nende olwa tsing’ining’ini tsitsia."